channel.title: Homestuck
channel.description:
[url]https://www.mspaintadventures.com[/url] It's a story about these 4 kids, and then there was 12 more and some other characters as well. It takes about 500 pages to pick up. But then shit gets shitten and shit is real. The Intermission is pretty good you should at least read that. [url]https://www.mspaintadventures.com/?s=6&p=003054[/url] Once in a while there will be these flash pages which are bees knees. [url]https://www.mspaintadventures.com/?s=6&p=003840[/url] Don't watch them all tho if you don't want to get major spoilers, like that flash spoils p.much everything that happens in act whogivesafuck.
There are like 4000 pages currently and there is a whole load of text in the form of logs(character development for +20 fags, do the maths)
Problem Sleuth is easier to read and more silly and less builduppy [url]https://www.mspaintadventures.com/?s=4&p=000219[/url]
yeah p.good
